<li><code class="language-none">&lt;update-download&gt;</code></li>
<li><code class="language-none">&lt;update-website&gt;</code></li>
<li><code class="language-none">&lt;dependencies&gt;</code></li>
<li><code class="language-none">&lt;publisher&gt;</code></li>
<li><code class="language-none">&lt;release-notes&gt;</code></li></ul></li>
<li>Since: OOo 2.2</li></ul>
<p><code class="language-none">&lt;description&gt;</code> is the root element of the update information XML document.
</p>
<table border="1" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse:collapse;">

<caption>Attribute &lt;description&gt;
</caption>
