<td>The namespace for dependency information (inherited from <code class="language-none">&lt;description&gt;</code>) must be defined as <a class="external free" href="http://libreoffice.org/extensions/description/2011">http://libreoffice.org/extensions/description/2011</a>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><code class="language-none">l:name</code>
</td>
<td>Required. The string ŌĆ£<code class="language-none">LibreOffice value</code>ŌĆØ (where value is the value of the attribute value).
