<td>Required. The required underlying LibreOffice version (ŌĆ£3.5ŌĆØ, ŌĆ£3.6ŌĆØ, etc.), starting with LibreOffice 3.5.
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h4><span id="Element_.2Fdescription.2Fdependencies.2FLibreOffice-maximal-version_2"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Element_/description/dependencies/LibreOffice-maximal-version_2">Element <code class="language-none">/description/dependencies/LibreOffice-maximal-version</code></span></h4>
