          <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>desc</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>Leaves which are assigned to this node. Extensions can add to this
            set new Leaf|s.<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>desc</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>info</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
