          <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>info</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
            <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>desc</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>Determines the position of the node in the options dialog.
