<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Absolute_Position_of_Leaves">Absolute Position of Leaves</span></h4>
<p>When one defines a Node and Leaf|s for this Node at the same time then one would like to specify the position of those leaves as well. This can be done be defining group of Leafs which has the same name as the Node to which they are assigned. This group is special because its Leafs are the first which appear under the corresponding node in the tree view. Otherwise the use of GroupIndex and GroupId is identical as explained in ŌĆ£Grouping of LeavesŌĆØ.
